communityDescription: GDG on Campus SGGSIE&T is a student-led community focused on empowering and connecting developers through Google technologies. We provide opportunities for learning, networking, and hands-on workshops to foster innovation and growth in the tech ecosystem

whatToExpect.title: Hackathons
whatToExpect.description: Test your skills in hackathons and coding challenges, pushing your limits while working on real-world projects and competing for exciting prizes!

whatToExpect.title: Workshops
whatToExpect.description: Join expert-led sessions on Android, Machine Learning, Web Tech, and Cloud Computing to sharpen skills with new tools and frameworks.

whatToExpect.title: Connections
whatToExpect.description: Explore valuable networking opportunities to connect with peers, exchange ideas, collaborate on projects, and expand your career prospects.

description.long: An annual event hosted by the Google Developers Group across the world to bring the technology closer to the developers.
